{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"down"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"node"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/DistributedActors\/documentation\/DistributedActors\/Node","preciseIdentifier":"s:17DistributedActors4NodeV","text":"Node"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Beware that this API is not very precise and, if possible, the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"down(Cluster.Member)"},{"type":"text","text":" is preferred, as it indicates"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the downing intent of a "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"specific"}]},{"type":"text","text":" actor system instance, rather than any system running on the given host-port pair."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This action can be performed by any member of the cluster and is immediately effective locally, as well as spread"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to other cluster members which will accept is as truth (even if they cal still reach the member and consider it as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".up"},{"type":"text","text":" etc)."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that once all members have seen the downed node as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".down"},{"type":"text","text":" it will be completely "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"removed"}]},{"type":"text","text":" from the membership"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and a tombstone will be stored to prevent it from ever “re-joining” the same cluster. New instances on the same host-port"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"pair however are accepted to join the cluster (though technically this is a newly joining node, not really a “re-join”)."}]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/distributedactors\/clustercontrol\/down(node:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/DistributedActors\/documentation\/DistributedActors\/ClusterControl\/down(node:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Mark "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"any"}]},{"type":"text","text":" currently known member as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Cluster.MemberStatus.down"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"down"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"node"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Node","preciseIdentifier":"s:17DistributedActors4NodeV"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}],"title":"down(node:)","roleHeading":"Instance Method","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","externalID":"s:17DistributedActors14ClusterControlV4down4nodeyAA4NodeV_tF","modules":[{"name":"DistributedActors"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/DistributedActors\/documentation\/DistributedActors","doc:\/\/DistributedActors\/documentation\/DistributedActors\/ClusterControl"]]},"references":{"doc://DistributedActors/documentation/DistributedActors":{"role":"collection","title":"DistributedActors","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/DistributedActors\/documentation\/DistributedActors","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/distributedactors"},"doc://DistributedActors/documentation/DistributedActors/ClusterControl/down(node:)":{"role":"symbol","title":"down(node:)","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"down"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"node"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Node","preciseIdentifier":"s:17DistributedActors4NodeV"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Mark "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"any"}]},{"type":"text","text":" currently known member as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Cluster.MemberStatus.down"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/DistributedActors\/documentation\/DistributedActors\/ClusterControl\/down(node:)","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/distributedactors\/clustercontrol\/down(node:)"},"doc://DistributedActors/documentation/DistributedActors/ClusterControl":{"role":"symbol","title":"ClusterControl","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"ClusterControl"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Allows controlling the cluster, e.g. by issuing join\/down commands, or subscribing to cluster events."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/DistributedActors\/documentation\/DistributedActors\/ClusterControl","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"ClusterControl"}],"url":"\/documentation\/distributedactors\/clustercontrol"},"doc://DistributedActors/documentation/DistributedActors/Node":{"role":"symbol","title":"Node","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"Node"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Node"},{"type":"text","text":" is a triplet of protocol, host and port that a node is bound to."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/DistributedActors\/documentation\/DistributedActors\/Node","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"Node"}],"url":"\/documentation\/distributedactors\/node"}}}